{"tid":1653563,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日做黨鐵同做黑警其實有冇分別？","createTime":"2019-10-14T06:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T06:49:45.000Z","uid":79382,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f74e8f7183fc9c9fa7bed6f0161371cebac709b8","tid":1653563,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"睇到隔離黨鐵interview post有感而發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前就話咩身在曹營心在漢，<br />\n831之後真係信唔過任何一個黨鐵職員<br />\n（當然我都由831起冇搭過）。<br />\n而家日撚日都大規模封站，<br />\n講真呢班所謂「後生黃」有冇據理力爭過？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警隊我都信3萬幾人入面<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可能</span></strong></span>有3個係正常人類嘅，<br />\n但講真你選擇留喺一個99.9%都係禽獸嘅團隊，<br />\n就唔好怪人當埋你係禽獸之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacd5eebdfeeee62aed89cc4881907f16ad59677","tid":1653563,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:44:47.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋都係聽上面做嘢<br />\n屌佢哋都冇撚用<br />\n有班人仲要係咁屌721元朗個女車長<br />\n明明人哋都自身難保隨時被打<br />\n仲要屌佢點解唔開車唔出嚟保護乘客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b2091f2fd4fbd8d906a8618f5a765ff9a7ad56","tid":1653563,"uid":137967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dacd5eebdfeeee62aed89cc4881907f16ad59677","tid":1653563,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:44:47.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋都係聽上面做嘢<br />\n屌佢哋都冇撚用<br />\n有班人仲要係咁屌721元朗個女車長<br />\n明明人哋都自身難保隨時被打<br />\n仲要屌佢點解唔開車唔出嚟保護乘客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:46:16.000Z","msg":"警察都係聽上面做野姐"},{"pid":"a4c0d1fb7d5d8e37c6bd6ff75cae64d4ea5420f3","tid":1653563,"uid":62841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"睇佢做成點囉 <br />\n有啲拆緊站嗰陣會提你快啲走 有啲小黃人唔捉跳閘 有啲會派出閘飛 <br />\n呢啲咪ok囉"}]}